title: Band of Skulls - Himalayan (2014) mp3@320kbps
description:
Produced by Nick Launay (Yeah Yeah Yeahs, Arcade Fire, Nick Cave and the Bad Seeds), 'Himalayan' is the follow up to 2011's 'Sweet Sour' and will be released on March 31, 2014. Scroll down for the full tracklisting for the record, which will be preceded by the single 'Asleep At The Wheel' on January 5, 2014. Watch the recently unveiled video at the bottom of the page. The band will tour the UK in March 2014, including two dates at London O2 Shepherd's Bush Empire. 

The 'Himalayan' tracklisting is:

'Asleep At The Wheel'
'Himalayan'
'Hoochie Coochie'
'Cold Sweat'
'Nightmares'
'Brothers And Sisters'
'I Guess I Know You Fairly Well'
'You Are All That I Am Not'
'I Feel Like Ten Men, Nine Dead And One Dying'
'Toreador'
'Heaven's Key'
'Get Yourself Together'
